> create host foo
> create tag bar
> host foo set description Great Scott!
> tag bar host add foo
> tag bar host list
foo
> tag bar show hosts
foo
> tag bar describe hosts
foo: Great Scott!

> tag bar show all
bar:
  hosts:
  - foo
  vars:
    isidore_tag_bar:
      description: null
      group: null

> tag bar host remove foo
> delete tag bar
Tag bar has been deleted.
> delete host foo
Host foo has been deleted.

